# ğŸ’» Technical Explanation

### Internal Network (VirtualBox me)

* VirtualBox ek **virtual switch** create karta hai.
* Jo bhi VMs us **Internal Network** se attach honge â†’ unko ek **same subnet** me IP milega.
* Sirf wo VMs apas me communicate kar sakte hain.
* Host machine aur Internet ka koi connection nahi hota.

ğŸ‘‰ Matlab ek **completely isolated private network**.

