# ğŸ“Š Example with IPs

Maan le tune ek Internal Network banaya â†’ `intnet` naam se.

* VM1 â†’ `192.168.100.2`
* VM2 â†’ `192.168.100.3`
* VM3 â†’ `192.168.100.4`

ğŸ‘‰ VM1 â†” VM2 â†” VM3 âœ… (Ping possible)
ğŸ‘‰ VM1 â†” Internet âŒ
ğŸ‘‰ VM1 â†” Host âŒ

